OL,3,CBA to run daily direct flights from
OL,4,CGuernsey to Europe's busiest airport
OL,6,FPeople in Guernsey will soon be able
OL,7,Fto get direct flights to Europe's
OL,8,Fbusiest airport.
OL,10,FBritish Airways will run year-round,
OL,11,Fdaily services to London Heathrow
OL,12,FTerminal Five from April 2026.
OL,14,FGuernsey's Economic Development
OL,15,FCommittee has signed an agreement to
OL,16,Fsupport the route in the hope of
OL,17,Fboosting business and tourism,
OL,18,Falthough it is not yet clear what, if
OL,19,Fany, financial subsidy has been given
OL,20,Fto the airline.
