OL,6,FCommittee President, Deputy Sasha
OL,7,FKazantseva-Miller, adds: "Connectivity
OL,8,Fis one of the most important economic
OL,9,Fdevelopment levers and a key priority
OL,10,Ffor the Committee this political term.
OL,12,F"In a week that has seen significant
OL,13,Fupheaval and disruption to air
OL,14,Fconnectivity in the Channel Islands, I
OL,15,Fhope that this agreement with help
OL,16,Fshape a new era."
OL,18,FThe announcement follows the airline
OL,19,FBlue Islands' sudden collapse last
OL,20,FFriday, which saw 1,200 passengers
OL,21,Fdisplaced and 21,000 bookings voided.
