OL,3,CBA to run daily direct flights from
OL,4,CGuernsey to Europe's busiest airport
OL,6,FBA is re-establishing its presence in
OL,7,Fthe island by offering a direct link
OL,8,Fto its home of operations and a wide
OL,9,Frange of international connections.
OL,11,FThe UK flag carrier will use Airbus
OL,12,FA319 and A320neo aircraft on its
OL,13,Froute, which can hold between 144 and
OL,14,F180 people.
OL,16,FNeil Chernoff, the company's Chief
OL,17,FPlanning and Strategy Officer, says:
OL,18,F"The addition of Guernsey is something
OL,19,Fwe know our customers have been
OL,20,Feagerly awaiting.
