OL,3,CBA to run daily direct flights from
OL,4,CGuernsey to Europe's busiest airport
OL,6,F"As the only direct service between
OL,7,FHeathrow and Guernsey, the route will
OL,8,Foffer conveniently timed connections
OL,9,Fto more than 20 European destinations,
OL,10,Fproviding greater choice and
OL,11,Fflexibility for both leisure and
OL,12,Fbusiness travellers alike."
OL,14,FFlights will depart Heathrow at
OL,15,F11:55am, arriving in Guernsey an hour
OL,16,Flater, before the return service at
OL,17,F1:50pm, landing back in London at
OL,18,F2:55pm.
