OL,3,CBA to run daily direct flights from
OL,4,CGuernsey to Europe's busiest airport
OL,6,FIn response, the Guernsey States-owned
OL,7,Fairline Aurigny, which runs up to nine
OL,8,Fflights a day to London City and
OL,9,FGatwick, says it is considering its
OL,10,Foptions for future services.
OL,12,FThe company's Chairman, Kevin George,
OL,13,Fadds: "While some changes represent
OL,14,Fopportunity, there are also material
OL,15,Frisks involved.
OL,17,F"The challenge with adding air
OL,18,Fconnectivity into an already-served
OL,19,Fmarket is to do so without taking away
OL,20,Ffrom what is already in place.
