OL,3,CBA to run daily direct flights from
OL,4,CGuernsey to Europe's busiest airport
OL,6,F"Our obligation is to highlight the
OL,7,Flikely implications to all our
OL,8,Fstakeholders and to take mitigating
OL,9,Faction to lessen the impacts on our
OL,10,Fbusiness.
OL,12,F"In the coming weeks, we will seek to
OL,13,Fwork with our shareholders on the
OL,14,Feffect that today's announcement may
OL,15,Fhave on our primary shareholder
OL,16,Fobjective of protecting Guernsey's
OL,17,FLondon connectivity. And, of course,
OL,18,Fwe will focus on managing the
OL,19,Fimmediate financial impact on our
OL,20,Fbusiness."
